short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Your own pair partner for learning

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Duo Drive, your personal learning assistant, is made to improve your educational experience by matching you with the ideal study partner for group projects. Duo Drive matches you with a learning partner who is compatible with your preferred method of learning, so you can work together to overcome obstacles, share knowledge, or just stay motivated.
